name: Sribalaji IInfotek
overview: Sri balaji founder of iinfotek has rich experience in oracle applications and a well versed technical expert in various technical areas viz hardware , networking, programming, consulting and excelled in the field of oracle applications techno functional consulting. He has experience in consulting division across countries like U.S, U.K, Dubai, Abu Dhabi, Africa, Egypt, Kenya, Nigeria, Indonesia, Jakarta, Singapore etc. He is an ex-oracle Singapore. He also worked as a corporate trainer in oracle training India division. His recent classes include oracle Romania, Europe. Now he imparts technical knowledge to the public candidates as well through various corporate sectors. He has an experience of more than 14 years.
